{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":882,"text":"So, I have a feature on my website where every week"},{"time":3391,"text":"people submit hypothetical questions"},{"time":5391,"text":"for me to answer,"},{"time":6979,"text":"and I try to answer them using math, science"},{"time":9360,"text":"and comics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":10820,"text":"So for example, one person asked,"},{"time":13228,"text":"what would happen if you tried to hit a baseball"},{"time":14922,"text":"pitched at 90 percent of the speed of light?"},{"time":17328,"text":"So I did some calculations."},{"time":20280,"text":"Now, normally, when an object flies through the air,"},{"time":22547,"text":"the air will flow around the object,"},{"time":24021,"text":"but in this case, the ball would be going so fast"},{"time":25950,"text":"that the air molecules wouldn't have time"},{"time":27401,"text":"to move out of the way."},{"time":29020,"text":"The ball would smash right into and through them,"},{"time":32007,"text":"and the collisions with these air molecules"},{"time":33668,"text":"would knock away the nitrogen,"},{"time":35333,"text":"carbon and hydrogen from the ball,"},{"time":37291,"text":"fragmenting it off into tiny particles,"},{"time":39128,"text":"and also triggering waves of thermonuclear fusion"},{"time":41612,"text":"in the air around it."},{"time":43140,"text":"This would result in a flood of x-rays"},{"time":45305,"text":"that would spread out in a bubble"},{"time":47056,"text":"along with exotic particles,"},{"time":48482,"text":"plasma inside, centered on the pitcher's mound,"},{"time":51602,"text":"and that would move away from the pitcher's mound"},{"time":55144,"text":"slightly faster than the ball."},{"time":57629,"text":"Now at this point, about 30 nanoseconds in,"},{"time":60311,"text":"the home plate is far enough away"},{"time":62214,"text":"that light hasn't had time to reach it,"},{"time":64120,"text":"which means the batter"},{"time":65571,"text":"still sees the pitcher about to throw"},{"time":68335,"text":"and has no idea that anything is wrong."},{"time":70352,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":72624,"text":"Now, after 70 nanoseconds,"},{"time":75050,"text":"the ball will reach home plate,"},{"time":76504,"text":"or at least the cloud of expanding plasma"},{"time":79241,"text":"that used to be the ball,"},{"time":81370,"text":"and it will engulf the bat and the batter"},{"time":85135,"text":"and the plate and the catcher and the umpire"},{"time":88596,"text":"and start disintegrating them all"},{"time":91401,"text":"as it also starts to carry them backward"},{"time":94567,"text":"through the backstop, which\nalso starts to disintegrate."},{"time":98031,"text":"So if you were watching this whole thing"},{"time":99801,"text":"from a hill,"},{"time":101108,"text":"ideally, far away,"},{"time":104481,"text":"what you'd see is a bright flash of light"},{"time":105936,"text":"that would fade over a few seconds,"},{"time":107442,"text":"followed by a blast wave spreading out,"},{"time":109570,"text":"shredding trees and houses"},{"time":112030,"text":"as it moves away from the stadium,"},{"time":114149,"text":"and then eventually a mushroom cloud"},{"time":117081,"text":"rising up over the ruined city. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":120842,"text":"So the Major League Baseball rules"},{"time":121998,"text":"are a little bit hazy,"},{"time":124102,"text":"but — (Laughter) — under rule 6.02 and 5.09,"},{"time":128987,"text":"I think that in this situation,"},{"time":130596,"text":"the batter would be considered hit by pitch"},{"time":133049,"text":"and would be eligible to take first base,"},{"time":135683,"text":"if it still existed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138886,"text":"So this is the kind of question I answer,"},{"time":140682,"text":"and I get people writing in with"},{"time":142821,"text":"a lot of other strange questions."},{"time":144695,"text":"I've had someone write and say,"},{"time":147242,"text":"scientifically speaking, what is the best"},{"time":149161,"text":"and fastest way to hide a body?"},{"time":151231,"text":"Can you do this one soon?"},{"time":153453,"text":"And I had someone write in,"},{"time":155313,"text":"I've had people write in about,"},{"time":157328,"text":"can you prove whether or not you can find love again"},{"time":159532,"text":"after your heart's broken?"},{"time":161204,"text":"And I've had people send in"},{"time":162979,"text":"what are clearly homework questions"},{"time":164970,"text":"they're trying to get me to do for them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168113,"text":"But one week, a couple months ago,"},{"time":171018,"text":"I got a question that was actually about Google."},{"time":174679,"text":"If all digital data in the world\nwere stored on punch cards,"},{"time":177645,"text":"how big would Google's data warehouse be?"},{"time":180324,"text":"Now, Google's pretty secretive\nabout their operations,"},{"time":183046,"text":"so no one really knows how much data Google has,"},{"time":186422,"text":"and in fact, no one really knows\nhow many data centers Google has,"},{"time":188937,"text":"except people at Google itself."},{"time":191428,"text":"And I've tried, I've met them a few times,"},{"time":192662,"text":"tried asking them, and they\naren't revealing anything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197885,"text":"So I decided to try to figure this out myself."},{"time":200420,"text":"There are a few things that I looked at here."},{"time":202579,"text":"I started with money."},{"time":204485,"text":"Google has to reveal how much they spend,"},{"time":206627,"text":"in general, and that lets you put some caps"},{"time":208617,"text":"on how many data centers could they be building,"},{"time":212403,"text":"because a big data center costs\na certain amount of money."},{"time":214703,"text":"And you can also then put a cap on"},{"time":217135,"text":"how much of the world hard\ndrive market are they taking up,"},{"time":219466,"text":"which turns out, it's pretty sizable."},{"time":221418,"text":"I read a calculation at one point,"},{"time":223355,"text":"I think Google has a drive failure"},{"time":224820,"text":"about every minute or two,"},{"time":228074,"text":"and they just throw out the hard drive"},{"time":229424,"text":"and swap in a new one."},{"time":230810,"text":"So they go through a huge number of them."},{"time":233010,"text":"And so by looking at money,"},{"time":234121,"text":"you can get an idea of how\nmany of these centers they have."},{"time":236970,"text":"You can also look at power."},{"time":238830,"text":"You can look at how much electricity they need,"},{"time":242727,"text":"because you need a certain amount\nof electricity to run the servers,"},{"time":244534,"text":"and Google is more efficient than most,"},{"time":246573,"text":"but they still have some basic requirements,"},{"time":249670,"text":"and that lets you put a limit"},{"time":251586,"text":"on the number of servers that they have."},{"time":253533,"text":"You can also look at square footage and see"},{"time":257724,"text":"of the data centers that you know,"},{"time":259000,"text":"how big are they?"},{"time":260353,"text":"How much room is that?"},{"time":261275,"text":"How many server racks could you fit in there?"},{"time":263635,"text":"And for some data centers,"},{"time":265338,"text":"you might get two of these pieces of information."},{"time":267327,"text":"You know how much they spent,"},{"time":269023,"text":"and they also, say, because they had to contract"},{"time":271380,"text":"with the local government"},{"time":272799,"text":"to get the power provided,"},{"time":274479,"text":"you might know what they made a deal to buy,"},{"time":277136,"text":"so you know how much power it takes."},{"time":278890,"text":"Then you can look at the ratios of those numbers,"},{"time":281184,"text":"and figure out for a data center"},{"time":282713,"text":"where you don't have that information,"},{"time":284349,"text":"you can figure out,"},{"time":285441,"text":"but maybe you only have one of those,"},{"time":287628,"text":"you know the square footage,\nthen you could figure out"},{"time":289307,"text":"well, maybe the power is proportional."},{"time":291630,"text":"And you can do this same thing\nwith a lot of different quantities,"},{"time":293950,"text":"you know, with guesses about\nthe total amount of storage,"},{"time":296026,"text":"the number of servers, the\nnumber of drives per server,"},{"time":298619,"text":"and in each case using what you know"},{"time":301666,"text":"to come up with a model that narrows down"},{"time":304193,"text":"your guesses for the things that you don't know."},{"time":306323,"text":"It's sort of circling around the\nnumber you're trying to get."},{"time":308588,"text":"And this is a lot of fun."},{"time":311143,"text":"The math is not all that advanced,"},{"time":313325,"text":"and really it's like nothing more than"},{"time":316460,"text":"solving a sudoku puzzle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318472,"text":"So what I did, I went through all of this information,"},{"time":323781,"text":"spent a day or two researching."},{"time":325540,"text":"And there are some things I didn't look at."},{"time":327579,"text":"You could always look at the Google"},{"time":330622,"text":"recruitment messages that they post."},{"time":332439,"text":"That gives you an idea of where they have people."},{"time":334377,"text":"Sometimes, when people visit a data center,"},{"time":335988,"text":"they'll take a cell-cam photo and post it,"},{"time":337833,"text":"and they aren't supposed to,"},{"time":339323,"text":"but you can learn things about\ntheir hardware that way."},{"time":342136,"text":"And in fact, you can just\nlook at pizza delivery drivers."},{"time":344689,"text":"Turns out, they know where all\nthe Google data centers are,"},{"time":347344,"text":"at least the ones that have people in them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350220,"text":"But I came up with my estimate,"},{"time":352405,"text":"which I felt pretty good about,"},{"time":354269,"text":"that was about 10 exabytes of data"},{"time":357518,"text":"across all of Google's operations,"},{"time":359940,"text":"and then another maybe five exabytes or so"},{"time":363372,"text":"of offline storage in tape drives,"},{"time":365417,"text":"which it turns out Google is"},{"time":366992,"text":"about the world's largest consumer of."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369502,"text":"So I came up with this estimate, and this is"},{"time":373063,"text":"a staggering amount of data."},{"time":374306,"text":"It's quite a bit more than any other organization"},{"time":377180,"text":"in the world has, as far as we know."},{"time":378927,"text":"There's a couple of other contenders,"},{"time":380673,"text":"especially everyone always thinks of the NSA."},{"time":383017,"text":"But using some of these same methods,"},{"time":384446,"text":"we can look at the NSA's data centers,"},{"time":386469,"text":"and figure out, you know, we\ndon't know what's going on there,"},{"time":388951,"text":"but it's pretty clear that their operation"},{"time":391041,"text":"is not the size of Google's."}]},{"cues":[{"time":392638,"text":"Adding all of this up, I came up with"},{"time":394377,"text":"the other thing that we can answer, which is,"},{"time":396273,"text":"how many punch cards would this take?"},{"time":398258,"text":"And so a punch card can hold"},{"time":401216,"text":"about 80 characters,"},{"time":403207,"text":"and you can fit about 2,000 or so cards into a box,"},{"time":406980,"text":"and you put them in, say,"},{"time":408254,"text":"my home region of New England,"},{"time":410206,"text":"it would cover the entire region"},{"time":412546,"text":"up to a depth of a little less than five kilometers,"},{"time":416020,"text":"which is about three times deeper"},{"time":417463,"text":"than the glaciers during the last ice age"},{"time":419862,"text":"about 20,000 years ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":422030,"text":"So this is impractical, but I think"},{"time":424453,"text":"that's about the best answer I could come up with."},{"time":427404,"text":"And I posted it on my website. I wrote it up."},{"time":429542,"text":"And I didn't expect to get an answer from Google,"},{"time":433232,"text":"because of course they've been so secretive,"},{"time":434863,"text":"they didn't answer of my questions,"},{"time":436267,"text":"and so I just put it up and said,"},{"time":437774,"text":"well, I guess we'll never know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":439297,"text":"But then a little while later"},{"time":441321,"text":"I got a message, a couple weeks later, from Google,"},{"time":443770,"text":"saying, hey, someone here has an envelope for you."},{"time":447212,"text":"So I go and get it, open it up,"},{"time":450013,"text":"and it's punch cards. (Laughter)"},{"time":452540,"text":"Google-branded punch cards."},{"time":455622,"text":"And on these punch cards,\nthere are a bunch of holes,"},{"time":458870,"text":"and I said, thank you, thank you,"},{"time":460171,"text":"okay, so what's on here?"},{"time":461690,"text":"So I get some software and start reading it,"},{"time":463320,"text":"and scan them, and it turns out"},{"time":465320,"text":"it's a puzzle."},{"time":466689,"text":"There's a bunch of code,"},{"time":468327,"text":"and I get some friends to help,"},{"time":469581,"text":"and we crack the code, and then\ninside that is another code,"},{"time":472133,"text":"and then there are some equations,"},{"time":473428,"text":"and then we solve those equations,"},{"time":474599,"text":"and then finally out pops a message from Google"},{"time":478070,"text":"which is their official answer to my article,"},{"time":481259,"text":"and it said, \"No comment.\""},{"time":483711,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":494292,"text":"And I love calculating these kinds of things,"},{"time":497509,"text":"and it's not that I love doing the math."},{"time":499224,"text":"I do a lot of math,"},{"time":500789,"text":"but I don't really like math for its own sake."},{"time":503865,"text":"What I love is that it lets you take"},{"time":505815,"text":"some things that you know,"},{"time":507215,"text":"and just by moving symbols\naround on a piece of paper,"},{"time":511993,"text":"find out something that you didn't know"},{"time":513690,"text":"that's very surprising."},{"time":515870,"text":"And I have a lot of stupid questions,"},{"time":517546,"text":"and I love that math gives the power"},{"time":519349,"text":"to answer them sometimes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522106,"text":"And sometimes not."},{"time":523633,"text":"This is a question I got from a reader,"},{"time":526557,"text":"an anonymous reader,"},{"time":527730,"text":"and the subject line just said, \"Urgent,\""},{"time":529775,"text":"and this was the entire email:"},{"time":531704,"text":"\"If people had wheels and could fly,"},{"time":534466,"text":"how would we differentiate them from airplanes?\""},{"time":537162,"text":"Urgent. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":539837,"text":"And I think there are some questions"},{"time":543190,"text":"that math just cannot answer."},{"time":545860,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":548331,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}